  <brief_title>Effects of a High Viscosity Dietary Fibre, as Part of a Medically Supervised Weight Management Program</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Controlled Trial Evaluating the Effects of a High Viscosity Dietary Fibre, as Part of a Medically Supervised Weight Management Program, on Body Weight in Overweight and Obese Individuals</official_title>
