  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI 27 - 30 Kg/m2 with 1 weight-related comorbidity and/or BMI 30 - 50 Kg/m2

          -  Ability to provide written informed consent in accordance with Good Clinical Practice
             (GCP) and local legislation in English

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Medications and supplements that affect body weight and appetite

          -  Type 2 diabetes on insulin treatment

          -  Contraindications to low calorie diet

          -  Any allergies to study product ingredients

          -  Any other medical, social or geographic condition, which, in the opinion of the
             investigator would not allow safe completion of the protocol.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
